# CVE-2026-41254 — liblcms2 (Little CMS) in the distroless runtime base.
# Fixed upstream in Debian 12 as 2.14-2+deb12u1; the pinned distroless
# java21-debian12:nonroot digest predates that rebuild. liblcms2 is dragged in
# by the JRE's java.desktop image I/O codecs, which this headless API never
# invokes — not reachable. Clears automatically on the monthly base digest
# refresh.
